OL,6,F2001 Following the takeover of HTV by
OL,7,FCarlton in October 2000, HTV's on air
OL,8,Fbranding remained untouched for a
OL,9,Fnumber of months.  Until now.
OL,10,F Adapted versions of the spinning
OL,11,Fhearts idents were aired for the
OL,12,Ffirst time today.  The new ident
OL,13,Fsequences featured the soundtrack
OL,14,Ffrom the Carlton idents used in the
OL,15,FMidlands and London.  And whilst they
OL,16,Fopened with the same visuals as the
OL,17,FLondon/Midlands idents, the initial
OL,18,Fanimation transitioned to the
OL,19,Fspinning hearts/HTV logo animation
OL,20,Ffrom the previous set of HTV idents.
